<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10407111>
    dc:description "Fig. 14. Distribution map of species of Coilodes Westwood, 1846. A. Coilodes bezerrai Basílio & Vazde-Mello sp. nov.; Coilodes castaneus Westwood, 1846; and Coilodes edeiltae Basílio & Vaz-de-Mello sp. nov. B. Coilodes fumipennis Arrow, 1909; Coilodes humeralis (Mannerheim, 1829); and Coilodes lunae Basílio & Vaz-de-Mello sp. nov. C. Coilodes mayae Basílio & Vaz-de-Mello sp. nov.;Coilodes niger (Mannerheim, 1829) stat. rev.; Coilodes ovalis Robinson, 1948; and Coilodes parvulus Westwood 1846. D. Coilodes punctipennis Arrow, 1909; Coilodes ravii Basílio & Vaz-de-Mello sp. nov.; and Coilodes skelleyi Basílio & Vaz-de-Mello sp. nov." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10407111/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10407089>
    dc:description "Fig. 5. Coilodes humeralis (Mannerheim, 1829), ♂ at DZUP from Baixo Gandu, Espírito Santo, Brazil (A, D), four different ♂♂ at DZUP from Curitiba, Brazil (B–C, E–G); graphical representation (H–I), and another ♂ at DZUP from Baixo Gandu, Espírito Santo, Brazil (J–K). A. Body, dorsal view. B. Body, ventral view. C. Head, dorsal view. D. Head, ventral view. E. Pronotum, dorsal view.F–K. Male genitalia. F. Dorsal view. G. Ventral view. H. Right paramere. I. Left paramere. J. Right side. K. Left side. Scale bars: A–B = 1 mm; C–E = 0.5 mm; F–K = 0.2 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10407089/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10407085>
    dc:description "Fig. 4. Coilodes fumipennis Arrow, 1909, ♂ at CEMT from Alta Floresta, Mato Grosso, Brazil (A, C, E), ♂ at CERPE from Rondônia, Brazil (B), ♂ at CERPE from Alta Floresta, Mato Grosso, Brazil (D); ♂ at CEMT from Rondônia, Brazil (F–G), graphical representation (H–I), and another ♂ at CEMT from Alta Floresta, Mato Grosso, Brazil (J–K). A. Body, dorsal view. B. Body, ventral view. C. Head, dorsal view. D. Head, ventral view. E. Pronotum, dorsal view. F–K. Male genitalia. F. Dorsal view. G. Ventral view. H. Right paramere. I. Left paramere. J. Right side. K. Left side. Scale bars: A–B = 1 mm; C–E = 0.5 mm; F–K = 0.2 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10407085/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10407105>
    dc:description "Fig. 12. Coilodes ravii Basílio & Vaz-de-Mello sp. nov., holotype ♂ (A–G, J–K) and graphical representation (H–I). A. Body, dorsal view. B. Body, ventral view. C. Head, dorsal view. D. Head, ventral view. E. Pronotum, dorsal view.F–K. Male genitalia. F. Dorsal view. G. Ventral view.H. Right paramere. I. Left paramere. J. Right side. K. Left side. Scale bars: A–B = 1 mm; C–E = 0.5 mm; F–K = 0.2 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10407105/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10407097>
    dc:description "Fig. 8. Coilodes niger (Mannerheim, 1829) stat. rev., two ♂♂ from Macaé de Cima, Nova Friburgo, Rio de Janeiro, Brazil, at CERPE (A–E) and at CEMT (F–G); another ♂ at CEMT from Nova Friburgo, Rio de Janeiro, Brazil (J–K); and graphical representation (H–I). A. Body, dorsal view. B. Body, ventral view. C. Head, dorsal view. D. Head, ventral view. E. Pronotum, dorsal view. F–K. Male genitalia. F. Dorsal view. G. Ventral view. H. Right paramere. I. Left paramere. J. Right side. K. Left side. Scale bars: A–B = 1 mm; C–E = 0.5 mm; F–K = 0.2 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10407097/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10407081>
    dc:description "Fig. 3. Coilodes edeiltae Basílio & Vaz-de-Mello sp. nov., holotype ♂ (A–G, J–K) and graphical representation (H–I). A. Body, dorsal view. B. Body, ventral view. C. Head, dorsal view. D. Head, ventral view. E. Pronotum, dorsal view.F–K. Male genitalia. F. Dorsal view. G. Ventral view.H. Right paramere. I. Left paramere. J. Right side. K. Left side. Scale bars: A–B = 1 mm; C–E = 0.5 mm; F–K = 0.2 mm." ;
